{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c@2.pkg/1772597519430/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597520276", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c@2.pkg/1772597519430/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597520276"}, "identifier": "f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>D:从材料中该市“无废城市”建设，持续打造特色模式，助力高质量发展与生态建设等信息可知，该市不断推动绿色低碳转型，落实创新、绿色、协调的新发展理念，故D符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>A:材料中未体现城乡融合发展、农业发展，故A不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>B:题干中未体现资源现状、无节制消耗资源，故B不符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>C:题干中未体现自然资源丰富、总量大、种类多，故C不符合题意;</p>\n\n<p>故本题选D。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（原创）某市要求各级各部门落实《某市“无废城市”建设提质增效实施方案（2024 - 2025 年）》，持续打造特色模式，助力高质量发展与生态建设，为全国“无废城市” 建设、大湾区 “无废试验区” 建设提供样本。这表明该市（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（原创）某市要求各级各部门落实《某市“无废城市”建设提质增效实施方案（2024 - 2025 年）》，持续打造特色模式，助力高质量发展与生态建设，为全国“无废城市” 建设、大湾区 “无废试验区” 建设提供样本。这表明该市（  ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["D"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c@2.pkg/item.json?v=1754820246956", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "choice_type": "character", "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>坚持以人民为中心，促进生态农业发展，加快城乡融合步伐</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>对资源的过度开放和无节制消耗严重影响经济的可持续发展</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": false, "text": "<p>自然资源丰富、总量大、种类多，为改善民生奠定物质基础</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 1, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<p>不断推动绿色低碳转型，落实创新、绿色、协调的新发展理念</p>\n"}], "prompt": "<p>（原创）某市要求各级各部门落实《某市“无废城市”建设提质增效实施方案（2024 - 2025 年）》，持续打造特色模式，助力高质量发展与生态建设，为全国“无废城市” 建设、大湾区 “无废试验区” 建设提供样本。这表明该市（&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "$RE0000", "$M003002000", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "5036342749", "$RE0200", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "$RE0201", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5", "44bee8bc-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "44bec0c6-54e6-11ed-9c34-850ba61fa9f4", "ff8080814371757b014390f883db0453", "6a74973a-0772-11ed-ac74-092ab92074e6", "e7bbce2c-0590-11ed-9c79-92fc3b3249d5"], "status": "ONLINE", "is_publish": false, "id": "f9c16989-d623-40d2-aea9-562cddfd8f0c", "global_title": {"zh-CN": "（原创）某市要求各级各部门落实《某市“无废城市”建设提质增效实施方案（2024 - 2025 年）》，持续打造特色模式，助力高质量发展与生态建设，为全国“无废城市” 建设、大湾区 “无废试验区” 建设提供样本。这表明该市（  ）"}, "global_desc